<refentry id="org.bus1.activator">
  <refmeta>
    <refentrytitle>org.bus1.activator</refentrytitle>
    <manvolnum>1</manvolnum>
  </refmeta>

  <refnamediv>
    <refname>org.bus1.activator</refname>
    <refpurpose>Bus Service Manager</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>

  <refsect1>
    <title>Description</title>
    <para>The <command>org.bus1.activator</command> connects the services
    to the bus. It receives the configuration for the bus services from the
    <citerefentry><refentrytitle>org.bus1.administrator</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry>.
    It creates a bus peer for every configured service and listens for incoming
    requests on these peers. Incoming messages cause the activator to execute
    the service and hand over the bus connection with the queued messages.</para>
  </refsect1>

